text: Delivery attempt notice says driver couldn't access building, but I was home all day. Doorbell camera shows no courier.
I'll review doorbell footage timestamps against courier's delivery scan. This appears to be a false attempt entry.
Wrong address on shipping label. Package sent to 123 Oak Street instead of 123 Elm Street. Different neighborhood entirely.
I can see the incorrect shipping label in our warehouse system. I'll intercept the parcel and correct the delivery address now.
Parcel weighing 15 lbs dispatched from Seattle warehouse. Tracking stuck on 'in-transit' for 8 business days.
I'm escalating to our logistics coordinator to prevent further rescheduling and lock in guaranteed delivery for Monday.
Package routing shows DHL rescheduled delivery three times. Original estimate was Thursday, now showing next Monday.
